<div class=" p-3">
    <h4 class="hyperion-css-ng0dgn" data-test-tag="paragraph-header">About Tips!</h4>
    <p class="borderColor borderWidth margin padding mqDark hyperion-css-wlaotw">At Expressnews we are constantly looking for new angles.</p>
    <p class="borderColor borderWidth margin padding mqDark hyperion-css-wlaotw"><p class="borderColor borderWidth margin padding mqDark hyperion-css-wlaotw">And as a reader, you are an important part of our news work. With our service Tell me! you can easily submit tips, pictures and videos. In our apps, we can also reach you with local push notifications and calls..</p>

</div>

<div class="p-3">
    <h5> <strong>What happens to my tip?</strong></h5>

    <p class="borderColor borderWidth margin padding mqDark hyperion-css-wlaotw">We read all the tips that are sent. If we judge your tip to be interesting, we will contact you via the contact channels you provided.</p>
    <p>When you send your picture or movie to Express News, you also give your permission for publication.</p>

    <h5>How is my information protected?</h5>
    <p>
        Express News guarantees all tips source protection, a constitutional right under the Freedom of Press Regulation. All tips are sent encrypted.

        Your identity is protected with us, but the editors may contact you for further information about your tip.
    </p>

    <p>
        If you want to remain anonymous also to the editorial staff, there are several other ways to contact us: you can call from a hidden number or email us from a temporary email address, such as hotmail or gmail.
    </p>

</div>

